Statistical analysis tool for Warhammer 40,000 and Age of Sigmar

To use this tool, please visit http://40k.ghostlords.com/dice/

This tool was created by Jonathan Polley to help enhance your enjoyment of Warhammer games. Please direct any feedback to 40k@ghostlords.com.
Warhammer 40000 and Age of Sigmar are copyright Games Workshop Limited.

To install, simply copy all html and js files into a directory and serve on the web, along with any dependencies.

This requires chart.js to function.
http://www.chartjs.org/
